66-1338.National ethanol promotion group; board; powers.

The board may appropriate funds and become a member of any national ethanol promotion group.

SourceLaws 1978, LB 424, § 20;Laws 1981, LB 80, § 6;R.S.1943, (1990), § 66-820;Laws 1993, LB 364, § 9.
